This is the XWiki Android client repositary

For testing
-----------
1. Download and setup Android Virtual device with the platform version of 2.2 and AVD name as "android2.2". Then run that newly created virtual device

2. In the terminal set up environmental variable "ANDROID_HOME" to the Android SDK directory
Example for linux users 
	export ANDROID_HOME=/home/xxx/(path to the android sdk folder)

3. Go to the source code directory
4. Run maven clean build by "mvn clean install"
5. For deploying application run "mvn android:deploy"
	This will install newly built Android .apk file to the virtual device named "android2.2"
5. Goto emulator and open the menu. Run "AndroidRest" application


